  "detailed_description": "Fiery Rivaz is a vertical and horizontal auto scrolling 3d shoot'em up with an emphasis on innovative level design and an enthralling soundtrack.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFiery Rivaz is a woman determined to save the world.<br />\r\nShe sets off with her spaceship to find the big eye, which controls the earthly world through illusions.<br />\r\nIn your spaceship you have 3 different weapons at your disposal, which you have to use in a targeted manner in order to pass the tests.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game Fiery Rivez has set itself the goal of resurrecting and modernizing the shmup genre.<br />\r\nMore innovations, variety and ideas are presented in a likeable 3D guise.<br />\r\nThe gameplay is action-packed, fast and intense.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 7 Levels (some vertical, some horizontal)<br />\r\n- 7 Cool soundtracks<br />\r\n- 3 Different weapons (spread, focus and x-ray)<br />\r\n- 3D Graphics<br />\r\n- Fullscreen",
  "about_the_game": "Fiery Rivaz is a vertical and horizontal auto scrolling 3d shoot'em up with an emphasis on innovative level design and an enthralling soundtrack.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFiery Rivaz is a woman determined to save the world.<br />\r\nShe sets off with her spaceship to find the big eye, which controls the earthly world through illusions.<br />\r\nIn your spaceship you have 3 different weapons at your disposal, which you have to use in a targeted manner in order to pass the tests.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game Fiery Rivez has set itself the goal of resurrecting and modernizing the shmup genre.<br />\r\nMore innovations, variety and ideas are presented in a likeable 3D guise.<br />\r\nThe gameplay is action-packed, fast and intense.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 7 Levels (some vertical, some horizontal)<br />\r\n- 7 Cool soundtracks<br />\r\n- 3 Different weapons (spread, focus and x-ray)<br />\r\n- 3D Graphics<br />\r\n- Fullscreen",
